channel.description:
I'm a little bit of "slavaboo" myself and wanted to make some kind of hard bass trap type thing and ended up with this. I might have broken my headphones but I think this turned out pretty good. Remember when its hardbass it is HARDBASS and the only version that I made is bass boosted because it can't be anything else.
